doc.title: iinkonzo zangaphandle
doc.description: Xa ucofa ikhonkco, unokwazisa inkonzo yangaphandle ukuba ikhonkco licofa.

service.title: Udinga inkonzo yangaphandle ukuphumeza lo msebenzi, sinikezela ngoguqulelo lwe-beta yenkonzo
service.linkExplain: Unokukhuphela isicelo esihambelanayo ngokwenkqubo yokusebenza oyisebenzisayo. Akuqinisekwanga ukuba inokuqhuba ngesiqhelo phantsi kwazo zonke iinkqubo ukuba ufumana iingxaki, ukuba uyakwazi ukuqonda i {{0}} ulwimi lwenkqubo, ungakhuphela ikhowudi yemvelaphi kwaye uyiqulunqe ngokwakho.
